<taxonomicName id="A7C1EB8D865CA7B5335BC5B8570F6F71" authority="Tsuneki, 1991" authorityName="Tsuneki" authorityYear="1991" class="Insecta" family="Trigonalyidae" genus="Jezonogonalos" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Jezonogonalos marujamanae" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="101" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="marujamanae">Jezonogonalos marujamanae</taxonomicName>
Tsuneki, 1991 [= 
<taxonomicName id="C5C67E079C4F6C28222E63CC1FC19CA6" family="Trigonalyidae" genus="J." higherTaxonomySource="treatment-meta" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="J. marujamae" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="101" rank="species" species="marujamae">J. marujamae</taxonomicName>
Tsuneki, 1991], by monotypy. Synonymized with 
<taxonomicName id="7F1023CD9787B4ABEBF2B085EF37CD57" authority="Schulz, 1906" authorityName="Schulz" authorityYear="1906" class="Insecta" family="Trigonalyidae" genus="Pseudogonalos" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Pseudogonalos" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="101" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">Pseudogonalos</taxonomicName>
Schulz, 1906, by Lelej (1995) and re-instated by 
<bibRefCitation id="0E5A6F5C37989CD0528CF0D2AF71CB19" DOI="https://doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.385.6560" author="Chen, H-Y" journalOrPublisher="ZooKeys" pageId="0" pageNumber="101" pagination="1 - 207" refId="B6" refString="Chen, H-Y, van Achterberg, C, He, J-H, Xu, Z-F, 2014. A revision of the Chinese Trigonalyidae (Hymenoptera, Trigonalyoidea). ZooKeys 385: 1 - 207, DOI: https://doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.385.6560" title="A revision of the Chinese Trigonalyidae (Hymenoptera, Trigonalyoidea)." url="https://doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.385.6560" volume="385" year="2014">Chen et al. (2014)</bibRefCitation>
